data.description: BACK ON MARKET, to no fault of the seller! This is a STUNNING one-owner home ready to celebrate the holidays in!! 4 BR home + loft with GUEST SUITE on the main is on a gorgeous lot in the highly sought-after community of Sweetbriar. You'll feel right at home greeted by a nicely landscaped and manicured front lawn and covered porch. You will find beautiful flooring, a large formal dining room, a living room, an open kitchen and a guest suite all on the main level.  The kitchen features beautiful cabinetry, granite countertops, luxury backsplash, and a breakfast area. The second level has 3 BR's plus a loft area, laundry room, and an additional balcony that's perfect for evening relaxing. The large primary bedroom features a true sitting room with walk-in closet and ensuite. The primary bath features a soaking tub and walk-in shower. This is an outdoor entertainer's dream! Every inch of this home has been meticulously well taken care of. Bring your best offer and let's get you settled!
